00002032                          1832  * Subroutine    : Get Random
00002032                          1833  * Description   : Improved pseudo-random number generator
00002032                          1834  *-----------------------------------------------------------
00002032                          1835  GET_RANDOM:
00002032  2239 000025A6           1836      MOVE.L  RANDOM_SEED,D1
00002038  2401                    1837      MOVE.L  D1,         D2
0000203A  EB8A                    1838      LSL.L   #5,         D2          ; Multiply by 32
0000203C  D282                    1839      ADD.L   D2,         D1
0000203E  2401                    1840      MOVE.L  D1,         D2
00002040  EE8A                    1841      LSR.L   #7,         D2          ; Add some high bits
00002042  B581                    1842      EOR.L   D2,         D1
00002044  0681 00003039           1843      ADD.L   #12345,     D1          ; Add constant
0000204A  23C1 000025A6           1844      MOVE.L  D1,         RANDOM_SEED
00002050  4E75                    1845      RTS
