00002098                          1877  * Subroutine    : EXIT
00002098                          1878  * Description   : Exit message and End Game
00002098                          1879  *-----------------------------------------------------------
00002098                          1880  EXIT:
00002098                          1881      ; Show if Exiting is Running
00002098  103C 000B               1882      MOVE.B  #TC_CURSR_P,D0          ; Set Cursor Position
0000209C  323C 4004               1883      MOVE.W  #$4004,     D1          ; Col 40, Row 1
000020A0  4E4F                    1884      TRAP    #15                     ; Trap (Perform action)
000020A2  43F9 000023F6           1885      LEA     EXIT_MSG,   A1          ; Exit
000020A8  303C 000D               1886      MOVE    #13,        D0          ; No Line feed
000020AC  4E4F                    1887      TRAP    #15                     ; Trap (Perform action)
000020AE  103C 0009               1888      MOVE.B  #TC_EXIT,   D0          ; Exit Code
000020B2  4E4F                    1889      TRAP    #15                     ; Trap (Perform action)
000020B4  FFFF FFFF               1890      SIMHALT
